Package: tbmater
Type: Package
Title: a wrapper package for the Zhou lab's tbmate tool
Description: Tabix is great, but is somewhat wasteful when all files are on the
             same discrete coordinate system.  tbmate (Tabix mate) addresses
             this issue by decoupling coordinates from data.
Version: 0.11.10
Date: 2020-11-10
Authors@R: person("Tim", "Triche, Jr.", role=c("aut", "cre"), email="trichelab@gmail.com")
Author: Tim Triche, Jr. [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Tim Triche, Jr. <trichelab@gmail.com>
URL: https://github.com/trichelab/tbmater
BugReports: https://github.com/trichelab/tbmater/issues
